scene.message:
Elly: ...Was that Nike?{nl}
The goddess of victory{nl}
from Greece...{nl}
That was me... I am her...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Nike...{nl}
The archetype of the Angel{nl}
in Christianity...{nl}
That is me... I am her...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: She's lost it.{nl}
Gone completely off the{nl}
deep end.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Huh!?{nl}
Oh — I'm sorry.{nl}
But I'm alright now.{waitkey}{clearbox}I am the Angel who brings{nl}
victory. From here on, I shall{nl}
protect you all!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I-is that so?{nl}
I thought I alone had{nl}
been chosen...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kirishima,{nl}
you've been having that{nl}
dream about the butterfly.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: How did you know?{nl}
I've been seeing it often,{nl}
ever since I first used{nl}
a Persona...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Forget that for a sec —{nl}
what brought you here?{nl}
Is it like this outside too?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yes, it's absolutely{nl}
crawling with Demons. And we{nl}
can't leave the city.{waitkey}{clearbox}I looked all around, but{nl}
the school seems to be the{nl}
only safe place left.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Right! But first,{nl}
let's go to the shrine.{waitkey}{nl}
Maki's mother has been hurt{nl}
and collapsed there.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hey!{nl}
Lead with that next time!{nl}
{ctl0f:1} Let's go help her!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Soft-hearted fools.{nl}
Still... Persona, and now{nl}
this bizarre phenomenon...{waitkey}{nl}
It's all too convenient...{nl}
What's really behind this?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonoda...{nl}
I'm definitely coming{nl}
for you...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: The shrine isn't{nl}
that far from school,{nl}
is it. No problem —at all!{waitkey}{ret}
